## âœ… Workflow: Always Follow These Steps

### Step 1: Gather Requirements

Before creating ANY presentation, ask these 6 questions:

| # | Question | Options |
| --- | --- | --- |
| 1 | **Topic & Objective** | What is the presentation about, and what action should the audience take? |
| 2 | **Number of Slides** | 5 (quick pitch) Â· 8-10 (standard) Â· 12-15 (comprehensive) |
| 3 | **Target Audience** | Executives Â· Investors Â· Clients Â· Students Â· Internal team |
| 4 | **Text Density** | Minimalistic Â· Balanced Â· Detailed |
| 5 | **Visual Style** | Corporate Â· Lifestyle Â· Tech Â· Abstract Â· Playful Â· Serious |
| 6 | **Logo Placement** | Top-right Â· Top-left Â· Bottom-right Â· Bottom-left Â· None |

